  "texts": [
    "We use the pre-trained language models from the huggingface API 61.",
    "Based on the statistics of our gold-standard dataset, we choose 512 as the maximum sequence length, 20 as the query length, and 100 as the answer length.",
    "After reviewing the hyperparameters utilized in various QA tasks as outlined in 25, 52, 53, 58, [62] [63] [64] [65] [66] [67], we set the document stride to 128 and opted for a batch size of 32, a learning rate of 3e -5, and a training epoch count of 5 for the training configurations.",
    "We performed all experiments using a single GPU on a Linux virtual machine with two GRID V100-32C GPUs.",
    "To assess the performance of QA models in extracting IDU-related information, we utilize strict matching criteria to compute the F1 score 68."
